h5. Problem Definition

At the moment, when the plugin did not start during startup, the error thrown in the log is very general. for example
{quote}
'com.atlassian.servicedesk.project-ui' - 'JIRA Service Desk Project Plugin'  failed to load.
{quote}
This could be caused by timeout or the plugin being disabled in the database.

h5. Suggested Solution

It would be great to have a more meaningful and specific error message thrown when plugins failed to load or start. This will help JIRA admin to identify the cause and proceed with the steps to fix.

